public static enum A_Request.E_RequestStatus extends Enum<A_Request.E_RequestStatus>
Defines the states that a request can be in. Grammatically these may request a little mental manipulation depending on the context. For example, TERMINATE may mean "to be terminated", "being terminated", or "terminated".
